reviewText: Thought it was great like watching the different pets that have been in the White House
Everything went will with the order.  I got it to show my residents that I work with at a retirement facility.  Good DVD!

I home school my children and thought this video might be a nice way to introduce the white house to my children.  My 10 year old liked it, but my younger ones did not.  My 10 year old will watch things repeatedly, but only watched this once even though she enjoyed it the first time.  We did not keep this one.  The cover looks modern and cute, but the dvd itself is a lot drier and less colorful.  Note:  We are not animal lovers.  Someone who loves animals might enjoy this more than we did.
